des: We play the best rock from the 80s through today! 97.5 The Rig is the awesomeness that radio once was - brought to you by folks who love everything about it. If you're in Alva, Oklahoma or the surrounding area, you can hear us on the air - live, loud, and local! Join the Crew and tune in!
